Inside forms you will find the .frm files
You can open them using Notepad++ or VB6 or edit using GIT editor
YOU ONLY NEED TO MODIFY THE BELOW
Code Explaination :-
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
question.Caption = "Which company creates the PlayStation line of consoles ?" //question
option1.Caption = "Sony" //options
option2.Caption = "Microsoft"
option3.Caption = "Sega"
option4.Caption = "Nintendo"
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FOR THE CORRECT OPTION GO(IN THIS CASE OPTION1) GO TO THE CLICK() FUNCTION AND ADD THIS CODE

option1.BackColor = RGB(0, 256, 0)//highlights it in green if selected(REPLACE OPTION1 WITH CORRECT OPTION)
option1.Enabled = False //diasbles the rest
option2.Enabled = False
option3.Enabled = False
option4.Enabled = False
fifty.Enabled = False
pss.Enabled = False
flp.Enabled = False
score = score + 10 //increases score
Sleep 2000
Me.Hide
GQ2.Show
End Sub
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FOR THE WRONG OPTIONS GO TO THE CLICK() FUNCTION AND ADD THIS CODE 

option2.BackColor = RGB(256, 0, 0)//highlights in red if selected
option1.BackColor = RGB(0, 256, 0)//highlights the correct option in green(REPLACE OPTION1 WITH CORRECT OPTION)
option1.Enabled = False//disables the rest
option2.Enabled = False
option3.Enabled = False
option4.Enabled = False
fifty.Enabled = False
pss.Enabled = False
flp.Enabled = False
score = score - 10
Sleep 2000
Me.Hide
GQ2.Show
End Sub
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
